name: Ascension
description:
It's a model mostly trained on free range non artist sourced women. Some men. I tried like contrast here with metallic metally things looking metally and dark thing things looking darkish. Mostly it's on women tho cause I like making pictures of women personally so there you go.

All test images are made with no embeddings. But of course those help so use the ones you like as many are out there.

This is a SD 2.1 768 model. I use it in the automatic 1111 web gui. You should not need a yaml with the updated version but should you then rename a yaml to the checkpoint name.

SD 2.1 stuff people have problems running and some vodoo can be needed. I run my batch file like this:

set COMMANDLINE_ARGS= --no-half --xformers --no-half-vae --disable-nan-check

That is the "bat" file and the commandline I use.

To use type a string of words in the box and see what happens.

Also does some NSFW. type nsfw in the little box with the words.

Merge credit dont credit whatever
